&lt;p&gt;We asked the customer to add read ahead to the debug log. (lctl set_param debug=+reada)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The debug log is available in the attached support bundle (from crash 2014-06-05-20:01:29).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Read-ahead settings:&lt;br/&gt;
----8&amp;lt; ----&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl get_param llite.&lt;b&gt;.max_read_ahead&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
llite.store1-ffff88120ee93c00.max_read_ahead_mb=40&lt;br/&gt;
llite.store1-ffff88120ee93c00.max_read_ahead_per_file_mb=40&lt;br/&gt;
llite.store1-ffff88120ee93c00.max_read_ahead_whole_mb=2&lt;br/&gt;
----8&amp;lt; ----&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;We asked the customer to take a look at the web server logs to see which files are accessed at the time of the crash. This is never the same file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4192&quot; title=&quot;NFS server crash while fsx runs on clients&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4192&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4192&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
